              <li><strong>"<a href="https://lishkee.bandcamp.com/album/layers-2?t=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Layers" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">𝓛𝓪𝔂𝓮𝓻𝓼</a>"</strong> (Demo Album, April 2017) - Nominated for Debut of the Year at Radio_Head Awards</li>
