            <p><strong>Vocals, Production, Instrumentation, Songwriting</strong></p>
            <p>Creates the vocal landscapes and lyrical content that define Lishkee's introspective character</p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">Radim Kocourek</h4>
            <p><strong>Production, Instrumentation, Songwriting</strong></p>
            <p>Handles instrumental composition, electronic production, and sonic experimentation</p>

            <p class="mt-4">Both members handle all aspects of their music production from their home studio in Brno, maintaining complete creative control over their artistic output.</p>
          </div>
