        <section id="creative-approach" class="glass-card p-6 space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent">CREATIVE APPROACH &amp; PHILOSOPHY</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-text/90 prose-p:mb-6 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
            <p>Lishkee's creative process embodies the DIY spirit, with all music created, recorded, and produced in their small bedroom studio.</p>

            <p>This intimate setting allows for spontaneous experimentation and detailed sonic sculpting, resulting in music that feels both carefully crafted and organically evolved.</p>

            <p>The duo's willingness to experiment is evident in tracks like "Silver (Modular Version)," where modular synthesizers were recorded in a single take, embracing the unpredictability of the technology. This approach reflects their broader aesthetic: balancing control with chance, structure with improvisation, and electronic elements with human warmth.</p>

            <p>Their collaboration with visual artists (photographer Tomáš Škoda), filmmakers (Petr Kačírka), and theater collectives demonstrates a multidisciplinary approach that extends beyond traditional band activities into the realm of multimedia art.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

