            <p><strong>Based in:</strong> Brno, Czech Republic</p>

            <p>Brno, the Czech Republic's second-largest city, has a thriving independent music and arts scene. The city is home to numerous cultural spaces, including the innovative Káznice community and cultural center where Lishkee has collaborated on theatrical productions.</p>

            <p>This rich cultural ecosystem has shaped Lishkee's artistic development and provided opportunities for experimental collaborations that blend music with visual arts, theater, and film.</p>
